{"tid":1897431,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】日本疫情擴散 IOC資深委員龐德：東奧或5月底定生死","createTime":"2020-02-25T17:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T02:46:40.000Z","uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e668598cbeb1073fa9db3838ba3992f3326f44fe","tid":1897431,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:23:03.000Z","msg":"國際奧委會（IOC）資深委員龐德承認，由於日本的新型冠狀病毒肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情仍有擴散跡象，東京奧運是否能夠如期在7月24日揭幕，仍有很多變數。他更透露，國際奧委會或可能在5月底決定東京奧運是否如期舉行，而一旦決定取消，未必會由其他城市接辦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200226/IOHRSHXEAEMZCWCFU5ZRVJILXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200226%2FIOHRSHXEAEMZCWCFU5ZRVJILXE%2F&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=a402cc4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200226%2FIOHRSHXEAEMZCWCFU5ZRVJILXE%2F&h=7acc9663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200226/IOHRSHXEAEMZCWCFU5ZRVJILXE/</a><br />\n<br />\n我已經預知到4月尾日本會連續14天0確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同中國2月底復工一樣係神跡"},{"pid":"b79a4b9863ff98690a688139d3bd5c6cea9cb0a0","tid":1897431,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}